00:00:08.442 --> 00:00:11.579 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Dio] Hey, Pucchi,
were you aware

00:00:11.613 --> 00:00:15.249 position:10% line:83% align:start
an average of 40,000 people
visit the Louvre per day?

00:00:15.282 --> 00:00:17.484 position:30% line:83% align:start
It's the most
sought-out museum on Earth.

00:00:18.185 --> 00:00:20.955 position:13% line:89% align:start
It opened August 10, 1793.

00:00:20.989 --> 00:00:23.257 position:24% line:83% align:start
So, this guarantees
that every single day,

00:00:23.290 --> 00:00:26.093 position:21% line:83% align:start
before they decide
to leave the museum behind,

00:00:26.126 --> 00:00:27.494 position:33% line:83% align:start
40,000 humans
will choose to see

00:00:27.529 --> 00:00:29.496 position:33% line:83% align:start
the Mona Lisa
and Venus de Milo.

00:00:30.130 --> 00:00:32.432 position:27% line:89% align:start
Fascinating, no?

00:00:32.466 --> 00:00:35.168 position:10% line:83% align:start
When you say "fascinating",
do you mean the numbers?

00:00:35.202 --> 00:00:37.104 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Dio] Let me clarify.

00:00:37.137 --> 00:00:38.640 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm marveling about
how brilliant artists

00:00:38.673 --> 00:00:40.775 position:13% line:89% align:start
can imbue their very souls

00:00:40.808 --> 00:00:43.611 position:21% line:83% align:start
into something seen
as merely cold and inanimate.

00:00:43.645 --> 00:00:47.347 position:19% line:83% align:start
As if they're Stands
that travel beyond time itself.

00:00:47.381 --> 00:00:48.482 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Dio] Wouldn't you agree?

00:00:49.316 --> 00:00:51.653 position:5% line:89% align:start
An intriguing thought, I admit.

00:00:51.686 --> 00:00:54.022 position:16% line:83% align:start
So, you're implying that
Leonardo Da Vinci

00:00:54.054 --> 00:00:56.658 position:13% line:83% align:start
and Alexandros of Antioch
are Stand Users?

00:00:56.691 --> 00:01:00.060 position:27% line:83% align:start
Yes, I'm talking
about you as well, Pucchi.

00:01:00.862 --> 00:01:01.996 position:5% line:89% align:start
Your Pale Snake has the ability

00:01:02.030 --> 00:01:05.465 position:19% line:83% align:start
to holy manifest souls
and preserve them.

00:01:06.366 --> 00:01:07.502 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:01:07.535 --> 00:01:09.938 position:13% line:83% align:start
What I'm saying is are you
going to betray me some day?

00:01:09.971 --> 00:01:12.640 position:30% line:83% align:start
Why haven't you
attacked me yet?

00:01:12.674 --> 00:01:14.976 position:27% line:83% align:start
You do know that
my weakness is the sunlight,

00:01:15.009 --> 00:01:18.012 position:10% line:83% align:start
which is why I sleep all day
in darkness.

00:01:18.046 --> 00:01:20.314 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Dio] You could easily
kill me in my sleep.

00:01:20.347 --> 00:01:23.051 position:21% line:83% align:start
If you take The World
by turning it into a disc,

00:01:23.083 --> 00:01:24.251 position:27% line:83% align:start
you can be King
almost instantly.

00:01:25.853 --> 00:01:26.688 position:35% line:89% align:start
Go ahead!

00:01:27.254 --> 00:01:28.221 position:19% line:89% align:start
[tense music playing]

00:01:31.759 --> 00:01:33.226 position:10% line:83% align:start
That's never crossed my mind
even once before.

00:01:35.162 --> 00:01:36.864 position:19% line:83% align:start
I have only admiration
for people

00:01:36.898 --> 00:01:38.332 position:10% line:89% align:start
who help nurture my growth.

00:01:38.365 --> 00:01:41.234 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Young Father Pucchi]
You are the king of kings.

00:01:41.268 --> 00:01:43.037 position:30% line:83% align:start
When it's over,
where will you be?

00:01:43.071 --> 00:01:44.706 position:16% line:83% align:start
I want to see it through
to the end.

00:01:45.740 --> 00:01:48.076 position:16% line:83% align:start
I love you with the same
reverence and passion

00:01:48.108 --> 00:01:49.209 position:30% line:89% align:start
as I love God.

00:02:04.559 --> 00:02:08.328 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Dio] Forgive me, it's quite
obvious now, I've insulted you.

00:02:08.362 --> 00:02:10.698 position:27% line:83% align:start
I never imagined
I would one day meet a human

00:02:10.732 --> 00:02:14.669 position:5% line:83% align:start
who could so effortlessly
put me at ease in conversation.

00:02:14.702 --> 00:02:16.236 position:21% line:83% align:start
You must understand
I was afraid of losing you.

00:02:17.939 --> 00:02:21.075 position:10% line:83% align:start
You'll become a noble priest
one day. I'm certain.

00:02:21.109 --> 00:02:23.077 position:30% line:83% align:start
Take that disc,
and do as you will.

00:02:23.111 --> 00:02:24.712 position:24% line:89% align:start
A token of apology.

00:02:24.746 --> 00:02:27.515 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Dio] I have released it
from my body to you.

00:02:27.548 --> 00:02:30.384 position:10% line:83% align:start
No matter where you may be,
you can be secure

00:02:30.417 --> 00:02:33.220 position:27% line:83% align:start
in knowing I will
always give you power.

00:02:38.526 --> 00:02:40.494 position:30% line:89% align:start
[F.F. screams]

00:02:40.528 --> 00:02:41.395 position:41% line:89% align:start
Jo...

00:02:43.031 --> 00:02:44.197 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:02:44.732 --> 00:02:48.569 position:35% line:83% align:start
[screams]
Jolyne!

00:02:53.273 --> 00:02:55.009 position:13% line:89% align:start
Listen to me, Pale Snake.

00:02:55.043 --> 00:02:58.245 position:7% line:83% align:start
Read the memories on that disc
and find out where Jolyne is.

00:02:59.580 --> 00:03:01.516 position:19% line:83% align:start
-[crackling on radio]
-[Weather Forecast] Talk to me.

00:03:01.549 --> 00:03:02.884 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:03:02.917 --> 00:03:04.217 position:10% line:89% align:start
What happened? Is that you?

00:03:04.251 --> 00:03:05.218 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:03:07.220 --> 00:03:10.490 position:33% line:83% align:start
Answer me!
Or can't you hear me?

00:03:10.525 --> 00:03:12.527 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Pale Snake] Why's the radio
randomly sitting here?

00:03:13.427 --> 00:03:16.030 position:19% line:83% align:start
Who's the guy talking?
I need to know.

00:03:16.064 --> 00:03:18.533 position:7% line:89% align:start
But who the hell is that? Who?

00:03:18.566 --> 00:03:19.232 position:33% line:89% align:start
[crackling]

00:03:20.434 --> 00:03:22.603 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:03:22.637 --> 00:03:23.571 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Weather Forecast]
Ah, of course!

00:03:24.072 --> 00:03:25.540 position:24% line:89% align:start
I understand now.

00:03:26.541 --> 00:03:29.209 position:27% line:83% align:start
It's a situation
where you can't respond.

00:03:29.242 --> 00:03:30.277 position:7% line:89% align:start
I just left the medical wing.

00:03:30.310 --> 00:03:32.880 position:33% line:83% align:start
That bastard!
It's Weather Forecast!

00:03:32.914 --> 00:03:33.915 position:35% line:89% align:start
I knew it!

00:03:33.948 --> 00:03:34.247 position:27% line:89% align:start
[thunder claps]

00:03:35.917 --> 00:03:38.753 position:10% line:89% align:start
Wait! Why is it raining now?

00:03:40.922 --> 00:03:43.725 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunts]
I must get the disc,

00:03:43.758 --> 00:03:45.660 position:33% line:89% align:start
[clattering]

00:03:46.094 --> 00:03:47.962 position:27% line:89% align:start
Damn! You bitch!

00:03:47.995 --> 00:03:50.765 position:10% line:83% align:start
She must have gotten Weather
Forecast to create this storm.

00:03:54.301 --> 00:03:56.571 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm coming after you.
You're not going anywhere.

00:03:56.604 --> 00:03:58.305 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groans]

00:03:58.338 --> 00:04:00.407 position:38% line:83% align:start
[grunts]
What's going on?

00:04:00.440 --> 00:04:02.910 position:21% line:83% align:start
I can't see a thing.
Where did you go?

00:04:05.278 --> 00:04:07.915 position:13% line:89% align:start
No! Now, there's fog, too.

00:04:07.949 --> 00:04:09.449 position:33% line:89% align:start
[clattering]

00:04:10.651 --> 00:04:14.421 position:5% line:83% align:start
There is a pattern to the sound
of those rocks pounding.

00:04:14.454 --> 00:04:16.758 position:7% line:89% align:start
It's Morse code. Decipher it!

00:04:16.791 --> 00:04:18.492 position:30% line:83% align:start
[F.F.] This fog
isn't thick enough.

00:04:19.127 --> 00:04:20.628 position:16% line:89% align:start
They're gonna catch me.

00:04:21.662 --> 00:04:23.631 position:33% line:83% align:start
Pale Snake's
true identity is...

00:04:24.132 --> 00:04:24.732 position:30% line:89% align:start
Father Pucchi!

00:04:24.766 --> 00:04:26.634 position:30% line:89% align:start
He knows now.

00:04:26.667 --> 00:04:28.636 position:24% line:83% align:start
That little wretch
blew my cover.

00:04:28.669 --> 00:04:31.172 position:19% line:83% align:start
Weather Forecast knows
who I am!

00:04:31.205 --> 00:04:32.807 position:33% line:89% align:start
[clattering]

00:04:36.177 --> 00:04:38.112 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
Five hundred three.

00:04:38.146 --> 00:04:39.479 position:16% line:89% align:start
Count the prime numbers.

00:04:40.014 --> 00:04:41.281 position:30% line:89% align:start
Five-oh-nine.

00:04:41.314 --> 00:04:42.850 position:16% line:89% align:start
Five hundred twenty-one.

00:04:43.818 --> 00:04:46.419 position:27% line:83% align:start
All prime numbers
and they can't be divided.

00:04:46.453 --> 00:04:48.355 position:13% line:83% align:start
The reason people succumb
to defeat...

00:04:49.356 --> 00:04:50.224 position:24% line:89% align:start
Five twenty-three.

00:04:50.258 --> 00:04:52.492 position:7% line:89% align:start
...is because of their shame.

00:04:52.527 --> 00:04:54.294 position:27% line:83% align:start
Shame so great,
it can kill them.

00:04:54.996 --> 00:04:56.296 position:27% line:89% align:start
Five forty-one.

00:04:57.231 --> 00:04:59.133 position:27% line:83% align:start
Because of shame,
guilt and disgrace

00:04:59.167 --> 00:05:01.202 position:21% line:83% align:start
that make one regret
their past actions.

00:05:01.235 --> 00:05:03.805 position:16% line:83% align:start
People become helpless,
and weak, and cave in.

00:05:04.739 --> 00:05:06.707 position:24% line:83% align:start
It wasn't a mistake
that I didn't notice

00:05:06.741 --> 00:05:07.809 position:24% line:89% align:start
the guard's radio.

00:05:07.842 --> 00:05:09.610 position:27% line:89% align:start
It was a trial.

00:05:09.644 --> 00:05:11.646 position:7% line:83% align:start
I have to use what I've learnt
to ensure victory.

00:05:11.679 --> 00:05:13.014 position:10% line:89% align:start
The only saving grace now is

00:05:13.047 --> 00:05:17.151 position:5% line:83% align:start
Jolyne Cujoh still doesn't know
who I really am.

00:05:17.185 --> 00:05:19.187 position:10% line:83% align:start
Therefore, it seems nothing
has meaningfully changed yet.

00:05:19.220 --> 00:05:22.557 position:21% line:83% align:start
I haven't completely
lost sight of her.

00:05:22.590 --> 00:05:23.991 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Father Pucchi]
The genuine victor

00:05:24.025 --> 00:05:27.327 position:13% line:83% align:start
is the one who can conquer
and control all living beings.

00:05:27.360 --> 00:05:29.030 position:16% line:89% align:start
[F.F. breathes heavily]

00:05:30.565 --> 00:05:32.533 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Weather Forecast] You managed
to make it out alive.

00:05:32.567 --> 00:05:32.934 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hey!

00:05:36.671 --> 00:05:38.539 position:24% line:83% align:start
Where are Jolyne
and the rest of them?

00:05:41.008 --> 00:05:42.143 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] Anastasia.

00:05:42.176 --> 00:05:45.680 position:10% line:83% align:start
I want you to know I owe you
a huge debt of gratitude.

00:05:45.713 --> 00:05:49.550 position:27% line:83% align:start
So, thank you!
You are why I made it this far.

00:05:49.584 --> 00:05:52.320 position:13% line:83% align:start
But still, why would you
go through all this for me?

00:05:52.352 --> 00:05:54.188 position:35% line:83% align:start
Finding out
Pale Snake's true identity

00:05:54.222 --> 00:05:58.092 position:13% line:83% align:start
and taking back my dad's
memories is only my business.

00:05:58.125 --> 00:05:59.359 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:05:59.392 --> 00:06:02.330 position:16% line:83% align:start
Jolyne, how do you still
not know the answer?

00:06:02.362 --> 00:06:04.397 position:16% line:83% align:start
I have made my feelings
for you clear.

00:06:04.431 --> 00:06:07.034 position:21% line:83% align:start
You've been amenable
to my company, mostly.

00:06:07.869 --> 00:06:08.870 position:19% line:89% align:start
I see it in your eyes.

00:06:12.740 --> 00:06:14.609 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia] That's
the real reason I'm here.

00:06:16.110 --> 00:06:18.079 position:35% line:83% align:start
This thing
is chewing on my hair.

00:06:18.112 --> 00:06:18.846 position:19% line:89% align:start
Why is it doing that?

00:06:18.880 --> 00:06:20.715 position:16% line:89% align:start
Sorry, but I don't know.

00:06:20.748 --> 00:06:22.516 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] You have no idea?

00:06:22.550 --> 00:06:24.952 position:13% line:83% align:start
You can see it's chomping
my hair like noodles.

00:06:25.385 --> 00:06:27.088 position:30% line:89% align:start
[birds cawing]

00:06:29.724 --> 00:06:31.792 position:5% line:89% align:start
And now, it's eating dirt, too.

00:06:31.826 --> 00:06:35.395 position:13% line:83% align:start
Maybe it really is a plant
after all. Feeding itself.

00:06:35.428 --> 00:06:37.430 position:38% line:83% align:start
But then
it falls asleep instantly.

00:06:38.431 --> 00:06:41.468 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia gasps]
Shh! Jolyne, get down.

00:06:41.502 --> 00:06:43.504 position:13% line:83% align:start
-Something's coming over.
-[breathes softly]

00:06:44.272 --> 00:06:46.274 position:10% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music playing]

00:06:46.307 --> 00:06:47.942 position:24% line:89% align:start
[leaves rustling]

00:06:49.577 --> 00:06:50.878 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia]
There's two of them,

00:06:50.912 --> 00:06:53.446 position:13% line:83% align:start
and they're already gotten
way too close for comfort.

00:06:54.282 --> 00:06:55.116 position:24% line:89% align:start
[breathes softly]

00:06:59.020 --> 00:06:59.520 position:24% line:89% align:start
[breathes heavily]

00:07:01.488 --> 00:07:02.455 position:27% line:89% align:start
F.F.! It's you!

00:07:03.456 --> 00:07:04.759 position:30% line:89% align:start
[F.F.] Jolyne.

00:07:04.792 --> 00:07:07.494 position:21% line:83% align:start
I finally found out
who the real Pale Snake is.

00:07:07.528 --> 00:07:09.730 position:16% line:83% align:start
And it's Father Pucchi,
seriously.

00:07:09.764 --> 00:07:11.666 position:33% line:89% align:start
[both gasp]

00:07:11.699 --> 00:07:13.601 position:33% line:83% align:start
He's the one
who did this to me.

00:07:13.634 --> 00:07:14.835 position:41% line:83% align:start
[F.F.]
I almost bit the dust.

00:07:16.003 --> 00:07:19.507 position:5% line:83% align:start
If Weather Forecast hadn't
shown up, I'd be dead for sure.

00:07:19.540 --> 00:07:20.541 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[groans]
-[Jolyne] F.F.!

00:07:22.276 --> 00:07:24.045 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm okay,
just had to ditch the skin.

00:07:24.078 --> 00:07:26.647 position:30% line:83% align:start
Were you guys
able to handle your side?

00:07:26.681 --> 00:07:28.950 position:33% line:83% align:start
What happened
to your right eye? Here.

00:07:28.983 --> 00:07:31.819 position:24% line:83% align:start
[F.F.] Let me see!
I'll treat it for you.

00:07:31.852 --> 00:07:34.255 position:38% line:83% align:start
Back up!
What you just said before...

00:07:34.288 --> 00:07:37.291 position:5% line:83% align:start
Yeah, that asshole priest,
he was trying to find the baby,

00:07:37.325 --> 00:07:40.428 position:27% line:83% align:start
but this time,
using D an' G's memories.

00:07:40.460 --> 00:07:43.431 position:19% line:83% align:start
All we have to do now
is hunt him down,

00:07:43.463 --> 00:07:45.032 position:10% line:89% align:start
with Weather Forecast, too.

00:07:45.066 --> 00:07:46.300 position:10% line:89% align:start
Victory's around the corner.

00:07:46.334 --> 00:07:47.535 position:19% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne gasps softly]

00:07:47.568 --> 00:07:48.669 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] Weather Forecast.

00:07:49.236 --> 00:07:51.639 position:38% line:89% align:start
Jolyne.

00:07:51.672 --> 00:07:54.275 position:21% line:83% align:start
Have all your wounds
from the factory healed up no?

00:07:54.308 --> 00:07:56.476 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, and yours?

00:07:56.510 --> 00:07:58.145 position:13% line:89% align:start
[soft piano music playing]

00:07:58.179 --> 00:07:59.380 position:16% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne breathes softly]

00:07:59.413 --> 00:08:01.449 position:27% line:89% align:start
[grunts softly]

00:08:01.481 --> 00:08:03.818 position:19% line:83% align:start
Excuse me! But what is
suddenly happening here?

00:08:03.851 --> 00:08:05.019 position:24% line:83% align:start
What do they think
they're doing?

00:08:05.052 --> 00:08:06.087 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hugging! You dumbass!

00:08:08.389 --> 00:08:11.158 position:35% line:83% align:start
I mean it.
Pull them apart right now!

00:08:11.192 --> 00:08:12.193 position:10% line:89% align:start
[F.F.] You want me to do it?

00:08:12.226 --> 00:08:13.794 position:7% line:89% align:start
Well, I certainly can't do it.

00:08:13.828 --> 00:08:15.830 position:16% line:83% align:start
Besides, we made a deal
that you would help.

00:08:15.863 --> 00:08:18.232 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now, hurry! He's getting
his scent all over her.

00:08:18.265 --> 00:08:19.499 position:16% line:89% align:start
Oh, cool it, crisscross.

00:08:19.533 --> 00:08:21.535 position:19% line:83% align:start
They're just saying hi
to each other.

00:08:21.569 --> 00:08:23.004 position:41% line:83% align:start
See!
They're finished.

00:08:23.037 --> 00:08:24.705 position:13% line:83% align:start
Quit getting your panties
in a bunch.

00:08:24.739 --> 00:08:25.873 position:30% line:83% align:start
We found out
Father Pucchi is the enemy,

00:08:25.906 --> 00:08:28.709 position:21% line:83% align:start
so save your tantrum
for another time, buddy.

00:08:28.743 --> 00:08:31.078 position:24% line:83% align:start
Pardon? But are you
actually talking back?

00:08:31.112 --> 00:08:32.580 position:10% line:89% align:start
What gives you the audacity?

00:08:32.613 --> 00:08:34.815 position:16% line:83% align:start
It seems you've totally
abandoned our contract.

00:08:34.849 --> 00:08:36.984 position:30% line:83% align:start
You're nothing
but lowly plankton.

00:08:37.018 --> 00:08:38.719 position:24% line:89% align:start
[breathes sharply]

00:08:38.753 --> 00:08:41.389 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia] Jolyne, now that
we know Pale Snake's identity,

00:08:41.422 --> 00:08:43.891 position:30% line:83% align:start
let's dispatch
our tiny companion. Yes?

00:08:44.959 --> 00:08:47.695 position:16% line:83% align:start
There's no need for it,
so I'll go handle it.

