Now, we can both
enter your world together.

00:17:32.052 --> 00:17:33.688 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hallelujah, beloved Dio!

00:17:36.925 --> 00:17:38.560 position:35% line:83% align:start
Anastasia!
[grunts]

00:17:39.426 --> 00:17:40.227 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:17:46.034 --> 00:17:49.938 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] No! Am I too late?
This can't be...

00:17:49.971 --> 00:17:52.574 position:13% line:89% align:start
Please, no! Tell me how...

00:17:52.607 --> 00:17:54.141 position:19% line:89% align:start
How could this happen?

00:17:54.576 --> 00:17:56.544 position:27% line:89% align:start
Help! Somebody!

00:17:56.578 --> 00:17:58.880 position:16% line:89% align:start
Is there anyone around?

00:17:58.913 --> 00:18:02.449 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm desperate! Guards!
Over here, hurry!

00:18:02.482 --> 00:18:05.019 position:24% line:83% align:start
Can anyone hear me?
We need a doctor.

00:18:05.053 --> 00:18:06.386 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Hey!
-[grunts]

00:18:06.420 --> 00:18:09.757 position:13% line:83% align:start
-[Anastasia] Diver Drive.
-[Jolyne] Someone help...

00:18:10.592 --> 00:18:12.125 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Hey, F.F.!
-Please, hurry! Someone!

00:18:13.226 --> 00:18:14.729 position:27% line:89% align:start
Can you hear me?

00:18:14.762 --> 00:18:16.430 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne screams]
Help us!

00:18:16.463 --> 00:18:18.165 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Anatasia] Jolyne's grieving.
She's in pain.

00:18:20.434 --> 00:18:22.870 position:16% line:83% align:start
[weak groan] This tragedy
happened all because of you.

00:18:24.505 --> 00:18:25.439 position:35% line:89% align:start
Damn it...

00:18:25.472 --> 00:18:27.207 position:33% line:89% align:start
I'm so cold.

00:18:27.240 --> 00:18:29.443 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm getting colder
with every passing moment.

00:18:30.612 --> 00:18:34.247 position:10% line:83% align:start
My heart has almost stopped
beating entirely already.

00:18:34.281 --> 00:18:35.917 position:27% line:83% align:start
Her father's disc
was put inside me.

00:18:35.950 --> 00:18:38.620 position:38% line:83% align:start
If I die,
which appears very likely,

00:18:38.653 --> 00:18:41.121 position:16% line:83% align:start
it, too, will certainly
perish forever.

00:18:43.024 --> 00:18:45.627 position:27% line:83% align:start
I truly struggled
to remove it from my body,

00:18:45.660 --> 00:18:48.663 position:21% line:83% align:start
but my consciousness
is almost gone.

00:18:49.496 --> 00:18:51.231 position:33% line:83% align:start
It appears
you're disintegrating

00:18:51.264 --> 00:18:53.735 position:7% line:89% align:start
and degenerating quickly, too.

00:18:53.768 --> 00:18:56.771 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'll give you all I have left,
but you must do this.

00:18:56.804 --> 00:18:59.574 position:7% line:89% align:start
I want you to use my intellect

00:18:59.607 --> 00:19:01.475 position:13% line:83% align:start
and whatever small flicker
remains of my life.

00:19:01.509 --> 00:19:03.377 position:27% line:89% align:start
Use everything!

00:19:04.311 --> 00:19:06.581 position:24% line:89% align:start
It's all yours now.

00:19:06.614 --> 00:19:08.816 position:16% line:83% align:start
You're going to use that
to reach inside my body

00:19:08.850 --> 00:19:13.220 position:19% line:83% align:start
and take the disc out,
because Jolyne needs it.

00:19:13.253 --> 00:19:15.657 position:16% line:83% align:start
Only you, the plankton,
can do this.

00:19:16.423 --> 00:19:20.160 position:16% line:89% align:start
F.F., please, answer me.

00:19:20.995 --> 00:19:23.798 position:38% line:83% align:start
Remember?
You and I made a deal.

00:19:23.831 --> 00:19:27.300 position:10% line:83% align:start
That you would hear and obey
all my orders.

00:19:27.334 --> 00:19:30.270 position:30% line:83% align:start
I won't let you
break our promise.

00:19:30.303 --> 00:19:32.305 position:16% line:89% align:start
You're going to live on.

00:19:32.339 --> 00:19:34.341 position:16% line:83% align:start
I don't care what you do
to my body.

00:19:35.143 --> 00:19:36.811 position:24% line:89% align:start
You have to hurry!

00:19:36.844 --> 00:19:38.513 position:19% line:89% align:start
My consciousness is...

00:19:38.546 --> 00:19:40.148 position:33% line:89% align:start
fading away.

00:19:40.180 --> 00:19:41.949 position:19% line:89% align:start
[somber music playing]

00:19:43.483 --> 00:19:46.854 position:27% line:83% align:start
[gasps] No! No,
this cannot be happening!

00:19:46.888 --> 00:19:48.856 position:35% line:89% align:start
Anastasia!

00:19:48.890 --> 00:19:51.759 position:10% line:89% align:start
[F.F.] You're wrong, Jolyne.

00:19:52.660 --> 00:19:53.661 position:21% line:89% align:start
Please, don't worry!

00:19:53.695 --> 00:19:56.064 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's not what you think.

00:19:56.097 --> 00:19:57.397 position:24% line:89% align:start
Look at the disc.

00:19:57.865 --> 00:19:59.332 position:24% line:89% align:start
Anastasia did it.

00:20:00.200 --> 00:20:02.537 position:19% line:83% align:start
He recovered the disc.
It's back.

00:20:03.171 --> 00:20:06.306 position:13% line:89% align:start
F.F., wait! Was that you?

00:20:06.339 --> 00:20:07.842 position:30% line:83% align:start
Are you the one
doing the talking?

00:20:09.043 --> 00:20:10.978 position:27% line:83% align:start
[F.F.] I think
what I was most afraid of

00:20:12.279 --> 00:20:13.715 position:24% line:83% align:start
was having to leave
my friends behind

00:20:13.748 --> 00:20:15.282 position:7% line:83% align:start
without even having any chance
to say goodbye to them.

00:20:16.918 --> 00:20:17.752 position:41% line:89% align:start
But...

00:20:18.385 --> 00:20:20.188 position:13% line:89% align:start
when the end finally came,

00:20:20.220 --> 00:20:22.523 position:19% line:83% align:start
I found the strength
and courage to do it.

00:20:22.557 --> 00:20:23.558 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:20:24.025 --> 00:20:25.660 position:38% line:89% align:start
Jolyne,

00:20:25.693 --> 00:20:27.862 position:16% line:83% align:start
when Anastasia comes to,
please tell him this.

00:20:27.895 --> 00:20:31.199 position:13% line:89% align:start
"Your body's yours alone.

00:20:31.231 --> 00:20:32.700 position:21% line:83% align:start
I patched and healed
your wounds

00:20:32.734 --> 00:20:34.569 position:19% line:83% align:start
with your intelligence
and your potent life force."

00:20:34.602 --> 00:20:36.771 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] Hey, wait a minute!

00:20:36.804 --> 00:20:40.541 position:21% line:83% align:start
What the hell are you
talking about? No! F.F., wait!

00:20:40.575 --> 00:20:42.744 position:16% line:83% align:start
[F.F.] Goodbye, Jolyne.
Thanks for everything!

00:20:43.410 --> 00:20:45.546 position:10% line:89% align:start
My time here is finally up.

00:20:46.547 --> 00:20:48.482 position:24% line:83% align:start
The one you know
as F.F. will disappear.

00:20:48.516 --> 00:20:49.684 position:16% line:89% align:start
What are you telling me?

00:20:49.717 --> 00:20:51.619 position:30% line:83% align:start
This is crazy!
I don't believe you!

00:20:52.252 --> 00:20:53.755 position:16% line:89% align:start
Jolyne, it's all right!

00:20:54.421 --> 00:20:56.557 position:7% line:89% align:start
What you see right now is me!

00:20:56.591 --> 00:20:58.593 position:7% line:89% align:start
This is my intellect, my soul.

00:21:00.595 --> 00:21:03.131 position:10% line:89% align:start
And it's proof I was alive.

00:21:03.164 --> 00:21:05.233 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'm... I'm gonna get your disc,
F.F.'s disc,

00:21:05.265 --> 00:21:06.399 position:19% line:89% align:start
back from that priest.

00:21:06.433 --> 00:21:08.569 position:7% line:89% align:start
No matter what! I promise you!

00:21:08.603 --> 00:21:10.571 position:16% line:83% align:start
You'll come back to life
and stay here.

00:21:10.605 --> 00:21:12.405 position:38% line:83% align:start
[F.F.]
But that'll be a different F.F.

00:21:14.274 --> 00:21:16.276 position:30% line:83% align:start
The me you know
won't be in there.

00:21:16.978 --> 00:21:18.278 position:21% line:89% align:start
This is the true me.

00:21:19.279 --> 00:21:20.280 position:13% line:89% align:start
I could just say goodbye.

00:21:22.950 --> 00:21:24.317 position:16% line:83% align:start
I couldn't have left you
without doing that.

00:21:26.020 --> 00:21:26.821 position:38% line:89% align:start
Jolyne.

00:21:28.288 --> 00:21:29.791 position:13% line:89% align:start
[F.F.] It's gonna be okay.

00:21:30.658 --> 00:21:32.459 position:7% line:89% align:start
And that's my promise to you.

00:21:33.594 --> 00:21:35.395 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm glad you finally got
the disc back.

00:21:35.428 --> 00:21:37.632 position:21% line:83% align:start
-[leaves rustling]
-[soft piano music playing]

00:21:41.135 --> 00:21:42.302 position:35% line:89% align:start
F.F., no!

00:21:45.139 --> 00:21:46.774 position:24% line:89% align:start
[shaking breaths]

00:21:46.808 --> 00:21:48.843 position:24% line:89% align:start
[cracking on radio]

00:21:50.678 --> 00:21:51.712 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Weather Forecast]
Come in, F.F.

00:21:51.746 --> 00:21:54.682 position:24% line:83% align:start
I can't track you.
Do you copy? Over.

00:21:55.348 --> 00:21:56.316 position:30% line:89% align:start
Where are you?

00:21:57.018 --> 00:21:59.854 position:41% line:83% align:start
[gasps]
F.F.? Hey!

00:21:59.887 --> 00:22:01.823 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Weather Forecast]
Come in, F.F.! Acknowledge!

00:22:04.826 --> 00:22:05.827 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jolyne] F.F.!

00:22:09.831 --> 00:22:12.667 position:24% line:83% align:start
["Distant Dreamer"
by Duffy playing]

